title: 5th Undergraduate Student Council
content: Hello, we are the Undergraduate Student Council. The motto of the 5th Undergraduate Student Council is to be able to become an organization that can communicate well with the students, being innovative in changing the school and the culture here at SUNY Korea, and lastly being a student friendly and kind group for all people to approach. We hope to communicate and live out a happy campus life with you all. Thank you and be history makers together.
